Interface PathJoins

All Superinterfaces:
Joins
All Known Implementing Classes:
SelectImpl, SelectImpl.SelectResult
interface PathJoins
extends Joins

Common joins interface used internally. Cannot be made an inner class because the outer class (Select) has to implement it.
